import React from 'react';

import Grid from '@material-ui/core/Grid';

import { 
    HeaderProfileContainer,
    GridContainer,
    FlagContainer,
    Capacete2,
    Capacete1,
    BronzeFlag,
    TextFlagContainer,
    Elo,
    Pdl,
    Queue
  } from './calculator-styles';

import bronzeflag from "assets/bronze_flag.svg";
import capacete1 from "assets/Bronze/Capacete_1.png";
import capaceteFlag from "assets/Bronze/Capacete_2.png";

const Calculator = () => {
  return (
    <HeaderProfileContainer>
      <GridContainer>
        <Grid container spacing={2}
          direction="row"
          justify="center"
          alignItems="center">
          <Grid item xs={3}>
            <FlagContainer>
              <Capacete1 src={ capacete1 }/>
              <BronzeFlag src={ bronzeflag } />
              <Capacete2 src={ capaceteFlag }/>
              <TextFlagContainer>
                <Elo>
                  FERRO IV
                </Elo>
                <Pdl>
                  FERRO IV
                </Pdl>
                <Queue>
                  Solo
                </Queue>
              </TextFlagContainer>
            </FlagContainer>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={3}>
            <FlagContainer>
              <BronzeFlag src={ bronzeflag } />
              <Capacete2 src={ capaceteFlag }/>
            </FlagContainer>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </GridContainer>
    
    </HeaderProfileContainer>
  );
}

export default Calculator;
